OL,5,C1
OL,7,FThe regulator, Ofgem, has announced it
OL,8,Fis dropping its price cap by 12.3%. In
OL,9,Freal terms that means a typical dual-
OL,10,Ffuel household in England, Scotland
OL,11,Fand Wales should see a drop of #238
OL,12,Fover the course of a year or around
OL,13,F#20 a month.
OL,15,FBut energy is not the only household
OL,16,Fbill which is expected to change come
OL,17,FApril 1 - council tax and tax free
OL,18,Fchildcare are also expected to be
OL,19,Fdifferent in the new financial year.
