OL,7,FWhat does the energy price cap drop
OL,8,Fmean?
OL,10,FOfgem said the drop in the energy cap
OL,11,Fwould see prices reach their lowest
OL,12,Flevel since Russia's invasion of
OL,13,FUkraine in February 2022, which caused
OL,14,Fa spike in an already turbulent
OL,15,Fwholesale energy market, driving up
OL,16,Fcosts for suppliers and customers.
