OL,7,FThe will fall by 12% on 1 April 2024,
OL,8,Fto #1,690 a year for a typical dual-
OL,9,Ffuel household paying by Direct Debit
OL,10,F(based on Ofgem's new, lower typical
OL,11,Fuse figures).JThe price cap will last
OL,12,Ffor three months. It is predicted to
OL,13,Ffall again in July 2024.
OL,15,FHow does the Energy Price Cap work?
OL,17,FThe price cap was first introduced by
OL,18,Fenergy regulator Ofgem on January 1,
OL,19,F2019.
