OL,7,FThe price cap sets a limit on the
OL,8,Fmaximum amount suppliers can charge
OL,9,Ffor each unit of gas and electricity
OL,10,Fyou use, and sets a maximum daily
OL,11,Fstanding charge.
OL,13,FThere's no upper threshold for what
OL,14,Fyou actually pay ` if you use more
OL,15,Fenergy, you'll pay more, use less and
OL,16,Fyou'll pay less.
