OL,7,FSpikes in energy costs, high inflation
OL,8,Fand increases to the National Living
OL,9,FWage have pushed up the cost of
OL,10,Fdelivering services, according to the
OL,11,FLocal Government Association.JThe
OL,12,FGovernment made an extra #600m
OL,13,Favailable to councils for the 2024/25
OL,14,Ftax year, but the County Councils
OL,15,FNetwork said they still face a budget
OL,16,Fshortfall of #1.1bn over the next two
OL,17,Fyears.
