OL,5,C1
OL,7,FCouncil tax is a fee you pay which
OL,8,Fhelps councils pay for the services
OL,9,Fthey provide.
OL,11,FExamples include bin collection,
OL,12,Flibraries, maintaining parks and
OL,13,Fsports centres, highway services,
OL,14,Fincluding street lighting and
OL,15,Fcleaning, and road maintenance.
OL,17,FThe amount of council tax you pay is
OL,18,Fdecided on which valuation band your
OL,19,Fproperty is, your personal
OL,20,Fcircumstances and how much the council
OL,21,Fneeds to fund its services.
